{"id":113401,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/10/简讯：中国要求网吧缴电影版权费/","date":"2010-10-14T21:13:52Z","modified":"2010-10-14T21:13:52Z","title":"简讯：中国要求网吧缴电影版权费","content":"<div>\n<p>中国要求从明年开始，网吧和长途大巴等都须缴纳电影版权费用。</p>\n<p>中国的长途大巴往往会在车上给乘客播放电影，而网吧则会有电影库供人选择播放。</p>\n<p>收费将在北京和上海等数省市试点。</p>\n<p>不过中国此前要求卡拉OK缴纳音乐版权费就遇到不少困难。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/7LQAe78tXQAAfTp_vUwcbB-BYBQ/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/7LQAe78tXQAAfTp_vUwcbB-BYBQ/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/7LQAe78tXQAAfTp_vUwcbB-BYBQ/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/7LQAe78tXQAAfTp_vUwcbB-BYBQ/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=0qX4gzzQ87c:QGMMDjwp-xo:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=0qX4gzzQ87c:QGMMDjwp-xo:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=0qX4gzzQ87c:QGMMDjwp-xo:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=0qX4gzzQ87c:QGMMDjwp-xo:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=0qX4gzzQ87c:QGMMDjwp-xo:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=0qX4gzzQ87c:QGMMDjwp-xo:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/0qX4gzzQ87c\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2010/1